snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Gameplay
snippet.description:
Minecraft Dungeons is a new action-adventure game set in the Minecraft Universe. But how do you keep gameplay surprising and rewarding? And how do you appeal to so many different play styles? Take a deep dive into the gameplay with the Dungeons dev team!
https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/about-dungeons
